# Active Subagent Count Logging

When spawning and completing subagents, always track active subagents and log the current total.

- On subagent start:
  - `activeAgents.add(agentId)`
  - `console.log("Active agents:", activeAgents.size)`
- On subagent completion:
  - `activeAgents.delete(agentId)`
  - `console.log("Active agents:", activeAgents.size)`
